source: base image on which customisation is made
build: place where you do customisations on your base image
provisioners: builtin and 3rd party plugins to run customisations during build block
communicator: communication provider to run commands during building image, eg: ssh, winrm
postprocessor: 


packer inspect
packer validate
packer hcl2_upgrade   #converts packer json file to hcl template


